<figureCitation box="[284,316,592,618]" captionStart="FIGURES 18–22" captionStartId="14.[151,270,1164,1188]" captionTargetBox="[160,1416,194,1127]" captionTargetId="figure-107@14.[160,1426,194,1161]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURES 18–22. Male genitalia of Bergiantina, schausi group. 18. B. schausi; 19. B. intermedia; 20. B. parva; 21. B. trita, type; 22. B. dolens, type. = carina; = knob; and = projection. Scale bars = 3 mm." pageId="7" pageNumber="31">20</figureCitation>
